Natrium chloratum, Natrium hydrooxydatum, Oleum phosphoratum,
Oleum Resinaeempyrheumaticum, Pastilli Hydrargyri bichlorati corrosivi.
Phosphorits, Pilulae Ferri carbonici, Resina elastica, Resina Podophylli,
